Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.95,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,My mind control doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:06.23,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,No, that can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:10.13,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,Sacrifices! I need more sacrifices! \NThat must be the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:18.39,Default,Lowell,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on? I thought \Nyou could control the Demon Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.60,Default,Lowell,0,0,0,,Why do you think I went \Nalong with your plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.96,Default,Lowell,0,0,0,,Do something about—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:24.88,Default,Lowell,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:28.61,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,More. I need more sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.41,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,So many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:37.05,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Demon Sword can't touch me. \NI can try as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:40.35,Default,Executioner,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just add more sacrifices and come back.
